collectionId.description: The CIDR collection ID. See the `aws.route53.CidrCollection` resource for more details.

locationName.description: The CIDR collection location name. See the `aws.route53.CidrLocation` resource for more details. A `location_name` with an asterisk `"*"` can be used to create a default CIDR record. `collection_id` is still required for default record.
